Part I - (Dataset Exploration Title)¶

by ((Chinonso Onu)¶

Introduction¶

This is PISA dataset a loan dataset that describes the details of loan given to individuals of various status in life, the dataset contains 113,3937 rows and 81 columns, including BorrowerAPR(Annual Percentage RAte), Borrower Income etc. the goal of this project is to analyzed this dataset with the data visualization process to generate good insight and find trends and patterns from the data to generate a substantial report. the questions answered will be:

  • What affects the borrower’s APR or interest rate?
  • What are the factors that affect a loan’s outcome status?
  • Are there differences based on how large the original amount issued as loan is?
